Modify/Create Survey

Tasks Breakdown with Time Estimates:

Note:  Time estimates include proper implementation and testing.

1. Implement multi-valued attributes
	a. display as check box
	b. create new table for each multi-valued attribute

	Time estimate: 2 hours

2.  Implement Survey/Project Type
	a.  Homeless, Veterans, etc

	Time estimate: 1 hour

2.  Modify Survey
	a.  Modify Question Grouping(add new group, edit existing, delete group)
	b.  Edit question text
	c.  Edit response options
	d.  Update existing clients responses to match new response order numbers
	e.  Edit/Add VI weight for a question
	f.  Store new attributes in EAV table.
	g.  Update VI configuration

	Time estimate: 12 hours

3.  Create Survey
	a.  Give survey a name
	b.  Create Question Groupings
	c.  Project Type
	d.  Add/Delete/Modify questions for each group
	e.  Same functionality as modify survey task(VI score updates, etc.)
	f.  Map question id's to client columns where client column exists.
		Otherwise, create new entry in the EAV table.

	Time estimate:  20 hours

	
